  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Climb, tumble, and rage — the ruthless obstacle race for bunnies with nerves of steel.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alone or online against up to 8 players: whoever reaches the top wins. Everyone else… falls down in spectacular fashion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master dangerous parkour routes, dodge nasty traps, and jump with the precision of a bunny on espresso. One wrong step, one jump too early and boom, back to the start.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge your friends, chase each other through chaotic levels, and fight for a spot on the global leaderboard. Only the fastest earn the title “Golden Bunny” complete with an epic fireworks show.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging climbing and parkour levels with fair checkpoints</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online multiplayer for up to 8 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Global leaderboard with time comparison</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traps, checkpoints, and wonderfully frustrating “One more try!” moments included</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Average playtime: 60–120 minutes… or hours? (highly dependent on fall rate 🐰💀)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How far will <strong>YOU</strong> get — and how many times will you have to start all over again?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Climb, tumble, and rage — the ruthless obstacle race for bunnies with nerves of steel.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alone or online against up to 8 players: whoever reaches the top wins. Everyone else… falls down in spectacular fashion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master dangerous parkour routes, dodge nasty traps, and jump with the precision of a bunny on espresso. One wrong step, one jump too early and boom, back to the start.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge your friends, chase each other through chaotic levels, and fight for a spot on the global leaderboard. Only the fastest earn the title “Golden Bunny” complete with an epic fireworks show.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging climbing and parkour levels with fair checkpoints</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online multiplayer for up to 8 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Global leaderboard with time comparison</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traps, checkpoints, and wonderfully frustrating “One more try!” moments included</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Average playtime: 60–120 minutes… or hours? (highly dependent on fall rate 🐰💀)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How far will <strong>YOU</strong> get — and how many times will you have to start all over again?</p>",
